<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" align="center" lang="en"><p>In Resolve 10.1 Shift D bypasses all grades on your timeline without putting red crosses on each node, so not obvious&#8230;..<a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23resolve&amp;src=hash" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://twitter.com']);">#resolve</a><br />
